      <meta name="description" content="Discover Dubai Marina Yacht Club, nestled within the heart of ‘new Dubai’. A prestigious 5 Gold Anchor award-winning marina recognised for the quality of services and facilities, perfectly located for ease of access to sea and transportation links. By day, a boater’s haven and by night a vibrant bustling nightlife waterfront." />
