</div>
</section><section class="wp-block-argc-intro-1 container text-center" id="Section0"><div class="container top-bottom-space"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-12  wow fadeInUp"><h1 class="main-title">Welcome to Dubai Marina Yacht Club</h1><div class="max-width"><p class="small-text mtp10">Discover Dubai Marina Yacht Club, nestled within the heart of ‘new Dubai’. A prestigious 5 Gold Anchor award-winning marina recognised for the quality of services and facilities, perfectly located for ease of access to sea and transportation links. By day, a boater&#8217;s haven and by night a vibrant bustling nightlife waterfront.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-left content-section overlapping-section container nonoverlap ranches-restaurant"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block" data-lazy-src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Berthing-LRL.jpg.webp"/><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Berthing-LRL.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block"/></noscript></div></div><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3"><div class="content-box  text-left text-sm-left"><div class="icon-image-block"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/noun_Anchor_182293-1.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/noun_Anchor_182293-1.svg"></noscript></div><h4 class="">Berthing</h4><div class="small-text desc">As a member you can benefit from 24/7 assistance from our dock hand and security teams, shuttles and ice deliveries.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="/berthing/" title="SEE MORE">SEE MORE</a></div></div></div></div></section><p></p><section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-right content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top mbp60"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3 order-last order-sm-first"><div class="content-box box-top-minus text-left text-sm-left"><div class="icon-image-block"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/noun_Anchor_182293-1.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/noun_Anchor_182293-1.svg"></noscript></div><h4 class="">Berthing Enquiry Form</h4><div class="small-text desc">For more information about our berthing packages, click on the button below and fill out the form. One of our Team will then be in touch with all the details.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="https://form.typeform.com/to/Ai6oaRCg?typeform-source=emaar-surveys.pro.typeform.com" title="ENQUIRY FORM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ENQUIRY FORM</a></div></div><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 order-first order-sm-last wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center" data-lazy-src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/DMYC-TYPEFORM-7.jpg.webp"/><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/DMYC-TYPEFORM-7.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center"/></noscript></div></div></div></div></section><section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-left content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block" data-lazy-src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Rally-LRL-copy.jpg.webp"/><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Rally-LRL-copy.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block"/></noscript></div></div><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3"><div class="content-box  text-left text-sm-left"><div class="icon-image-block"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/icon-Events-Copy-2.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-dubaimarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/icon-Events-Copy-2.svg"></noscript></div><h4 class="">Rally Programme</h4><div class="small-text desc">A fun and memorable yachting experience visiting coastline locations around the UAE with like-minded boaters.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="/rallies/" title="SEE MORE">SEE MORE</a></div></div></div></div></section><div class="wp-block-group d-none"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"><section class="offerbox">

